{"tid":1383954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩冷氣軍師入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-29T20:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:55:04.000Z","uid":53666,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"872052fb56e8f3cd4a1f8b3164eaed6852b0925b","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:43:58.000Z","msg":"日撚日見到有呢啲post<br />\n<br />\n內容三句唔埋二句就話 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">DLLM 你班人推前線去死。</span></strong>」</span><br />\n<br />\nDLLM， 我依家就代表勇武手足正式推你哋出嚟接受軍事審判！<br />\n<br />\nsorry 講錯, 係無需審判，直接槍決！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有你哋呢種諗法嘅人，已經直接露底，根本就係一班陰魂不散嘅大台撚，以為己係大台，用大台嘅角度諗嘢， 情形 就好似藍屍話有人收錢搞破壞一樣，<br />\n<br />\n但係， <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">你哋比藍屍廢老更惡毒！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n藍屍廢老尚且識反對暴力。你哋卻要利用黑警暴力，去成全你哋嘅陰謀論！ 垃圾都不如。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你哋話任何一個手足喺今次運動嘅犠牲 係因為有人推佢哋去死， <br />\n<br />\n先不論係咪真係有人咁做，<br />\n你哋嘅潛台詞就係話佢哋只不過係卒，係condom。仲抵死過啲狗。<br />\n<br />\n黑警為咗份狗糧，出賣良知，甘願被洗腦，然後全世界睇住佢哋畀人推出嚟去死。如果有日有黑警冚旗，呢啲叫抵死。<br />\n<br />\n恕我已經諗唔到，有咩係可以比抵死更不堪，<br />\n<br />\n而係被你哋用嚟套在所有前線手足嘅犧牲之上。<br />\n<br />\n越諗越火！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我再講一次， <br />\n<br />\n任何策略上嘅建議，任何人都可以提出，畀大家參考，<br />\n<br />\n你哋亦可以哀求前線手足 三思而行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何人再用 「睇清楚你哋比人推去死咋！ 」<br />\n<br />\n呢種垃圾說法，我同所有光復香港嘅手足將會記錄低，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將來逐一處決！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nDLLM!"},{"pid":"a30cd540e18f4d90c7f9df7dffd9b30dd6799df5","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:45:32.000Z","msg":"無軍師夠膽入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05236d8b52df7594e69f130a490e6d4a92aa606d","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:56:21.000Z","msg":"對唔住太憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n天琦話過，不能被眼前憤怒所控制。要時刻保持清醒、警覺。<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n<br />\n我收返以上 將來逐一處決嘅言論。<br />\n<br />\n改成 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將來逐一審判！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0e6535e4d01e3ea497d1af02e8e4cb02cb296a","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:57:10.000Z","msg":"附上無待堂既文：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dadazim/photos/a.205214762897610/2320597731359292/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdadazim%2Fphotos%2Fa.205214762897610%2F2320597731359292%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=ba4fc63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dadazim/photos/a.205214762897610/2320597731359292/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"ad768ef287523530b8de8b7b060ecd126689f753","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:57:49.000Z","msg":"【長文請細讀】劉細良建議　我有唔同看法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f8c2ff4095838cf16a576c1ea8f64b19035a223","tid":1383954,"uid":198869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:00:18.000Z","msg":"終於有人屌"},{"pid":"aea518a2b5b911ed193083b8397ad37b92b386a2","tid":1383954,"uid":187538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl