r />\n又要學生犧牲多啲時間出嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:18:03.000Z","msg":"好心痛。光復香港，對抗極權，<br />\n<br />\n點解承擔最多，付出最多嘅要係呢一班年輕人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:21:48.000Z","msg":"接受唔到大條道理話班行最前線嘅學生 癡線"},{"pid":"ac2d64ab54d02de593894e180ad8a3434ce32e33","tid":1383954,"uid":198869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T21:41:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81dc3bfd90fa164a73c06075a80528189ea52386","tid":1383954,"uid":125154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535f701a6f9169da96d8f1c9fb5a78a623380c8b","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81dc3bfd90fa164a73c06075a80528189ea52386","tid":1383954,"uid":125154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"講得好好<br />\n<br />\n勇武先係現場嘅帶領者。<br />\n你哋嘅責任無比重大,<br />\n基本上所有人都係圍住你哋, <br />\n<br />\n你哋進, 大家就跟住進,<br />\n你哋退, 大家就會跟住退。<br />\n<br />\n最需要BE water 嘅係你哋。"},{"pid":"34e4b54bf0fd42192ec876fc117cb8fe571694ac","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"無咗勇武, <br />\n唔通用大愛感化班黑社會?<br />\n用道德感化班黑警?<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解200萬加一都無用?<br />\n呢個世界, 一切鬥爭升級嘅過程, 就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武力對決嘅過程</span></span>。 <br />\n最後只係雙方鬥癲、鬥唔怕死、鬥不惜一切。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命, 本來如是。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲有想講, <br />\n今日嘅港豬 同大陸低端人口 其實無本質上嘅分別ga..<br />\n港豬只不過係一班仲有得食有得玩嘅低端人口。<br />\n某程度上, 和理非都一樣,<br />\n喺極權面前, 和理非只不過一群仲有得拎道德嚟打飛機嘅低端人口。<br />\n<br />\n原因就係, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你一日非暴力, 一日就無人會怕你哋!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cd454831a31811691e091169bd600bd27cfa061c","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32d23a441e489b6f07df583d23cffa7ec0665714","tid":1383954,"uid":198869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cda9252a6971a5f2ebbdcaf512be83e6c1eabdac","tid":1383954,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d23a441e489b6f07df583d23cffa7ec0665714","tid":1383954,"uid":198869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到黑警雙手奉上委任証為止！"}]}